%% Diagram: Diagram 2
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant D as Driver
    participant L as Loc Svc
    participant R as Redis

    loop every 4-5s
        D->>L: GPS update
        L->>L: H3 (res 9)
        L->>R: GEOADD + EXPIRE 30s
    end
    Note over R: Match Svc: GEORADIUS (3km)
